.TH REDMINE2ABRAFLEXI-INVOICE 1 "2026-05-01" "Redmine2AbraFlexi 2.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
redmine2abraflexi-invoice \- Generate AbraFlexi invoice from Redmine workhours
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B redmine2abraflexi-invoice
[\fB\-o\fR \fIfilename\fR | \fB\-\-output\fR=\fIfilename\fR]
[\fB\-e\fR \fIfilename\fR | \fB\-\-environment\fR=\fIfilename\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B redmine2abraflexi-invoice
is a command-line tool that generates an invoice in AbraFlexi from the hours worked in Redmine.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-o\fR \fIfilename\fR, \fB\-\-output\fR=\fIfilename\fR
Write the result to the specified file (or stdout if omitted).
.TP
\fB\-e\fR \fIfilename\fR, \fB\-\-environment\fR=\fIfilename\fR
Load environment configuration from the specified file. Defaults to \fB.env\fR.
.SH SEE ALSO
The source code and documentation are available at <https://github.com/VitexSoftware/Redmine2AbraFlexi>.
.SH AUTHOR
Vítězslav Dvořák <info@vitexsoftware.cz>
